    "claim": "`redeemCollateral()` trusts the external `_totalFeePct` argument and computes `EXCHANGE_PRECISION - _totalFeePct` without checking that the fee is at most 100%. Any handler bug or bad upstream input that supplies `_totalFeePct > 1e18` causes an underflow revert.",
